quran[25{c,v,t}:
76,26,Wa minal laili fasjud lahoo wa sabbihhu lailan taweelaa
76,27,Inna haaa'ulaa'i yuhibboona 'aajilata wa yazaroona waraaa'ahum yawman saqeelaa
76,28,Nahnu khalaqnaahum wa shadadnaaa asrahum wa izaa shi'naa baddalnaaa amsaala hum tabdeelaa
76,29,Inna haazihee tazkiratun fa man shaaa'at takhaza ilaa rabbihee sabeela
76,30,Wa maa tashaaa'oona illaa anyyashaaa'al laah; innal laahaa kaana'Aleeman Hakeema
76,31,Yudkhilu many yashaaa'u fee rahmatih; wazzaalimeena
77,1,Wal mursalaati'urfaa
77,2,Fal'aasifaati 'asfaa
77,3,Wannaashiraati nashraa
77,4,Falfaariqaati farqaa
77,5,Falmulqiyaati zikra
77,6,'Uzran aw nuzraa
77,7,Innamaa too'adoona lawaaqi'
77,8,Fa izam nujoomu tumisat
77,9,Wa izas samaaa'u furijat
77,10,Wa izal jibaalu nusifat
77,11,Wa izar Rusulu uppitat
77,12,Li ayyi yawmin ujjilat
77,13,Li yawmil Fasl
77,14,Qa maaa adraaka maa yawmul fasl
77,15,Wailuny yawma 'izillilmukazzibeen
77,16,Alam nuhlikil awwaleen
77,17,Summa nutbi'uhumul aakhireen
77,18,Kazzlika naf'alu bilmujrimeen
77,19,Wailunw yawma 'izil lil mukazzibeen
